text: Tatiana Shishkova is a road cyclist from Moldova and Russia. She represented Moldova at the 2004 UCI Road World Championships and Russia at the 2006 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:Moldovan female cyclists Category:Russian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Date of birth missing (living people) Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
